^ "Luca Maestri". www.bloomberg.com. Bloomberg Businessweek. Retrieved 4 December 2014. 
^ "Luca Maestri". www.apple.com. Apple Inc. Retrieved 4 December 2014. 
^ "Luca Maestri". www.forbes.com. Forbes. Retrieved 4 December 2014. 
^ "Apple officially appoints new CFO Luca Maestri as Peter Oppenheimer transitions out". AppleInsider. Retrieved 2015-12-09. 









